strings: <voice_0x010013DC><se_high>Dye: C'mon... rub my nose so I don't get it.
<voice_0x010013DE><se_low>January: meaning<:> ah? I already have a girlfriend. Hurts too? Everything is good, even in the end.
<voice_0x010013DF><se_high>Dye: Oh, please don't go to Mindian Street. It can be difficult to be “responsible” to your loved one.
<voice_0x010013E0><se_high>Dye: Gordon Bennett, you don't even have to look in the mirror!
